      "created_at": "2022-01-04T20:30:28.268Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi!<br>\nJust a quick (and maybe silly\u2026) question\u2026<br>\nI\u2019m interested in this app, but after reading the website and forums I still don\u2019t know something mandatory to me:<br>\nCan I control the resistance (slope simulation) of my smart trainer throught this app?</p>\n<p>And another question related: If I upload a GPX files, the app can use the slope of the GPX track uploaded to modify the resistance of my trainer?</p>\n<p>Thanks in advance (\u2026and sorry for my not perfect english\u2026 is not my main lenguage\u2026)</p>",
